      "text": [
        " «يَمْسَحُهَا بِالْمَاءِ وَ لاَ يُعِيدُ اَلْغُسْلَ»."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2543 - Abu Ja'far (as) was asked about a man who performed ghusl for his ihram and then trimmed his nails.\nImam (as) replied: \"He should wipe them with water and does not need to repeat the ghusl.\""
        ]
      }
